  43,24,"Each ňĻwarnerňļ asked, ‚ÄúEven if what I brought you is better guidance than what you found your forefathers practicing?‚ÄĚ They replied, ‚ÄúWe totally reject whatever you have been sent with.‚ÄĚ"
